<!-- start quote section -->
<div class='row'>
  <div class='large-12 columns text-center quote'>
    <h3>"We've wired our world to share...creating an economy of 'what's mine is yours.'"</h3>
    <h5>Rachel Botsman, "The Case of Collaborative Consumption"</h5>
  </div>
</div>
<hr />
<!-- end quote section -->

<!-- value proposition start -->
  <div class="large-12 columns">
    <h3 class='text-center'>Reduce Clutter, Save Money</h3>
    <br />

    <div class="row">

      <div class="large-4 small-12 columns value">
        <%= image_tag 'bike_500_square.jpg' %>
        <h6 class="">
          Do you need to drill a hole, learn to surf, or go for a bike ride? Do you you value experiences and relationships more than more stuff in your house? Join OfferUp! and participate in the world of collaborative consumption. You need the hole, not the drill. 
        </h6>
      </div>

      <div class="large-4 small-12 columns value">
        <%= image_tag 'surf_500_square.jpg' %>
        <h6 class="">
         The products we buy sit unused for most of their lifetimes. This idle capacity represents a huge opportunity to participate in the share economy, to source and borrow goods from your neighbors and friends. Value doesn't have to cost money!
        </h6>
      </div>

      <div class="large-4 small-12 columns value">
        <%= image_tag 'mower_500_square.jpg' %>
        <h6 class="">
          OfferUp! is on a mission to make sharing cool. We're social, local and all about meaningful connections. Peer-to-peer product sharing can change the world, one Offer at a time. We want to help you do it...join today and get in on the action!
        </h6>
      </div>

    </div>
    <br />
    <div class='row text-center'>
    <%= link_to 'SIGN UP', new_user_path, class: 'button large-3 columns large-centered' %>
  </div>
</div>

<hr />
